# ── Cross-cutting alignments to ai: governance dimensions ────────────────────
# Maps ITIL practices and principles to canonical ai: dimensions for SPARQL
# queries that cross both the SKMS and domain layers.

itil:KnowledgeManagement          skos:relatedMatch ai:Transparency .
itil:InformationSecurityManagement skos:exactMatch  ai:Security .
itil:RiskManagement               skos:exactMatch  ai:Accountability .
itil:ServiceContinuityManagement  skos:relatedMatch ai:Robustness .
itil:AvailabilityManagement       skos:relatedMatch ai:Reliability .
itil:WorkforceAndTalentManagement skos:relatedMatch ai:HumanOversight .
itil:MeasurementAndReporting      skos:relatedMatch ai:Transparency .
itil:ServiceLevelManagement       skos:relatedMatch ai:Reliability .
itil:SupplierManagement           skos:relatedMatch ai:Accountability .
itil:FocusOnValue                 skos:relatedMatch ai:Sustainability .
itil:OptimiseAndAutomate          skos:relatedMatch ai:Sustainability .
